name: MobiNets
body:
### Welcome to MobiNets.
MobiNets is a research group targeting at the cutting-edge topics in the area of next-generation mobile internet, including SDN, NFV, Wireless Networks, Wireless Sensing, etc.
Our group now works in UESTC@China.
